     FBRIDF     UF   E           K DISK    USROPN
     FSVTHA2    IF   E           K DISK    USROPN
     FSVTFI     IF   E             DISK    USROPN
     FTRACKF    IF A E             DISK    USROPN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Variables common to all CGIs
