      /free
        JSONstring='{'
        +'¬user¬ : ¬'+%trim(WSUSER)+'¬, '
        +'¬usrAS400¬ : ¬'+%trim(WSUSR4)+'¬, '
        +'¬errMsg¬ : ¬'+%trim(Error)+'¬, ';
      /end-free
      * JSONfix escaper " i tekst,  for deretter å bytte ¬->"
     c                   call      'JSONFIX'
