      *********************************************************
     C     Parse         Begsr
      *********************************************************
      * Get input
     C                   EVAL      WSUSER  = zhbgetvar('user')
     C                   EVAL      WSUSR4  = zhbgetvar('usrAS400')
     C
     c                   endsr
      *********************************************************
     C     INIT          Begsr
      *********************************************************
     C                   OPEN      BRIDF
      * Test innlogging
     C     WSUSER        CHAIN     BRIDF                              50
     C     BILIBL        ifeq      *blanks
     C                   callb     'INCGI'
     C                   parm                    BISTDL
     C                   else
     C                   call      BILIBL
